  "detailed_description": "Cabbagers is multiplayer combat game about bunch of adult fellas from a neighborhood who play knights like children do.<br><br>The goal of the game is very simple - to beat other players with your mighty wooden sword.<br>There are no dull stats or rules for you to analyze. You just join the game and have fun.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/a7ca29cfaf83d72c3e82a4846d08e57c.poster.avif?t=1673532842\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/a7ca29cfaf83d72c3e82a4846d08e57c.webm?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/a7ca29cfaf83d72c3e82a4846d08e57c.mp4?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game is built upon P2P (peer-to-peer) network architecture. You can either host your own or join publicly available game session.<br>I am building community via Discord. I invite you to join my channel: . Feel free to leave a comment in <strong>#game-events </strong> that you are looking for someone to play with. <br><br>Before each game you pick one of four Cabbagers. Each character has a distinct personality, but plays the same. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/3ec4c8bad8add675e807ceb326fdaedd.poster.avif?t=1673532842\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/3ec4c8bad8add675e807ceb326fdaedd.webm?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/3ec4c8bad8add675e807ceb326fdaedd.mp4?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The combat is unique and satysfying. You can feel the impact of each strike. The player has a full control over the character's rotation which enables a precise whacks and dodges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/e25ba7f8b1a1be9a4e702f797f267bc1.poster.avif?t=1673532842\" width=360 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/e25ba7f8b1a1be9a4e702f797f267bc1.webm?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/e25ba7f8b1a1be9a4e702f797f267bc1.mp4?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game features original emote and voice system that allows for countless of funny interactions between players.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/02820a4ff01944a3a3e08aa179ac60cc.poster.avif?t=1673532842\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/02820a4ff01944a3a3e08aa179ac60cc.webm?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/02820a4ff01944a3a3e08aa179ac60cc.mp4?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>We can't wait to meet you here! Tons of fun and laughter guaranteed!",
  "about_the_game": "Cabbagers is multiplayer combat game about bunch of adult fellas from a neighborhood who play knights like children do.<br><br>The goal of the game is very simple - to beat other players with your mighty wooden sword.<br>There are no dull stats or rules for you to analyze. You just join the game and have fun.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/a7ca29cfaf83d72c3e82a4846d08e57c.poster.avif?t=1673532842\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/a7ca29cfaf83d72c3e82a4846d08e57c.webm?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/a7ca29cfaf83d72c3e82a4846d08e57c.mp4?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game is built upon P2P (peer-to-peer) network architecture. You can either host your own or join publicly available game session.<br>I am building community via Discord. I invite you to join my channel: . Feel free to leave a comment in <strong>#game-events </strong> that you are looking for someone to play with. <br><br>Before each game you pick one of four Cabbagers. Each character has a distinct personality, but plays the same. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/3ec4c8bad8add675e807ceb326fdaedd.poster.avif?t=1673532842\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/3ec4c8bad8add675e807ceb326fdaedd.webm?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/3ec4c8bad8add675e807ceb326fdaedd.mp4?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The combat is unique and satysfying. You can feel the impact of each strike. The player has a full control over the character's rotation which enables a precise whacks and dodges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/e25ba7f8b1a1be9a4e702f797f267bc1.poster.avif?t=1673532842\" width=360 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/e25ba7f8b1a1be9a4e702f797f267bc1.webm?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/e25ba7f8b1a1be9a4e702f797f267bc1.mp4?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game features original emote and voice system that allows for countless of funny interactions between players.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/02820a4ff01944a3a3e08aa179ac60cc.poster.avif?t=1673532842\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/02820a4ff01944a3a3e08aa179ac60cc.webm?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180610/extras/02820a4ff01944a3a3e08aa179ac60cc.mp4?t=1673532842\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>We can't wait to meet you here! Tons of fun and laughter guaranteed!",
